{"tw": {"3597020": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Becoming a King", "steam_appid": 3597020, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4075330, 4072680, 4072690, 4072700], "detailed_description": "<h1>👑BECOMING A KING EMPEROR`s EDITION👑</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/36aaaec4106f66664208d1f7b05f0010.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></p><br><h1>💖 ADD OUR GAMES TO YOUR WISHLIST 💖</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/cad06fc41403ffc9f6022411bd620695.avif?t=1771400693\" width=616 height=224 /></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/154e0bf082122d5387e32b34e7fc3a3a.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=357 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《王者歸來》中，掌控自己的命運！這是一款驚險刺激的情色冒險遊戲，並融入了時間管理元素！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《王者歸來》中，你將從卑微的出身開始，一路攀升，最後登上王位。管理你的時間，做出決定命運的選擇，證明你配得上王位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >錯綜複雜的陰謀、激情四射的愛情和艱難的困境正在等著你——你的王朝的未來掌握在你的手中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/1b824b9175bd7406223b765e727d4052.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💕 七位充滿魅力、令人難忘的女主角，與你展開浪漫之旅…或開啟一段更進一步的旅程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎬 全動畫H場景和可解鎖的收藏卡牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 不僅能建立浪漫關係，還能建立深厚的友誼</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏳ 引人入勝的時間管理機制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 扣人心弦的故事情節，充滿了政治陰謀和詭計</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 支線活動，包括迷你遊戲和自動戰鬥模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚖️ 由角色屬性和決策驅動的選擇系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/32d7556861e9e231a6f11327e990db74.poster.avif?t=1771400693\" width=754 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/32d7556861e9e231a6f11327e990db74.webm?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/32d7556861e9e231a6f11327e990db74.mp4?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一步都決定王國的命運！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充滿活力的地點，與當地人交流，加深關係，提升你的實力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刻苦訓練，揭開隱藏的秘密，贏得盟友－你需要他們所有人才能登上王位！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/c11bc5001e214936b5e027233966fa4d.poster.avif?t=1771400693\" width=754 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/c11bc5001e214936b5e027233966fa4d.webm?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/c11bc5001e214936b5e027233966fa4d.mp4?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/bb983d576d9d298992c796867e462a6c.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙魅力四射、風格各異的女孩——每個人都有自己的故事、秘密和閃光點</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙 贏得她的芳心，打造出堪比王冠的傳奇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙 出乎意料的轉折，揭開皇室的秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙 獨特的禮物、親密的約會和難忘的時刻</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙 考驗你們感情的情感障礙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💫 選擇你未來的女王，跟隨她的心意－寫下你自己的皇室愛情故事！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/e9e4f87e5eb89115955c53dca8e41d3b.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=420 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/4de5ab768a5618cd4fce831a38fea16e.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你會成為怎樣的國王？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你會揭開父母死亡背後的真相嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你會找到真愛──還是迷失在誘惑之中？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的僕人會尊重你……還是畏懼你？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一個選擇都會決定你的命運。明智選擇－你的王冠就在於此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/a43738f4fbb9e4d7c09bf71c6ac0f59b.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=488 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/154e0bf082122d5387e32b34e7fc3a3a.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=357 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《王者歸來》中，掌控自己的命運！這是一款驚險刺激的情色冒險遊戲，並融入了時間管理元素！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《王者歸來》中，你將從卑微的出身開始，一路攀升，最後登上王位。管理你的時間，做出決定命運的選擇，證明你配得上王位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >錯綜複雜的陰謀、激情四射的愛情和艱難的困境正在等著你——你的王朝的未來掌握在你的手中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/1b824b9175bd7406223b765e727d4052.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💕 七位充滿魅力、令人難忘的女主角，與你展開浪漫之旅…或開啟一段更進一步的旅程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎬 全動畫H場景和可解鎖的收藏卡牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 不僅能建立浪漫關係，還能建立深厚的友誼</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏳ 引人入勝的時間管理機制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 扣人心弦的故事情節，充滿了政治陰謀和詭計</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 支線活動，包括迷你遊戲和自動戰鬥模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚖️ 由角色屬性和決策驅動的選擇系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/32d7556861e9e231a6f11327e990db74.poster.avif?t=1771400693\" width=754 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/32d7556861e9e231a6f11327e990db74.webm?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/32d7556861e9e231a6f11327e990db74.mp4?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一步都決定王國的命運！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充滿活力的地點，與當地人交流，加深關係，提升你的實力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刻苦訓練，揭開隱藏的秘密，贏得盟友－你需要他們所有人才能登上王位！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/c11bc5001e214936b5e027233966fa4d.poster.avif?t=1771400693\" width=754 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/c11bc5001e214936b5e027233966fa4d.webm?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/c11bc5001e214936b5e027233966fa4d.mp4?t=1771400693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3597020/extras/bb983d576d9d298992c796867e462a6c.avif?t=1771400693\" width=1200 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙魅力四射、風格各異的女孩——每個人都有自己的故事、秘密和閃光點</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙 贏